headline.main: ISLAND IS GOVERNED BY AMERICAN SOLDIER; Identity Concealed Because Fall Is Unknown to Germans

lead_paragraph: WITH THE MEDITERRANEAN FLEET, Monday, Nov. 1 (Reuter) -- An American soldier is acting as Governor of an island that the Germans do not yet know has been occupied.
abstract: US soldier acts as gov of island occupied by Allies without Gers knowledge; occupation described
